<!-- Explore the world -->
<section id="explore" style="padding-bottom: 80px">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
          <h2 class="section-heading">Explore the world </h2>
          <h3 class="section-subheading text-muted" style="padding-bottom: 30px">See where people are traveling, all around the world</h3>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row text-center">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <h4 class="location-tag">New York City</h4>
        <%= image_tag("nyc.jpg", size: '335x344', class: "img-circle") %>
        <p class="text-muted" style="padding-top: 50px">Home to the Empire State Building, Times Square, Statue of Liberty and other iconic sites, New York City is a fast-paced, globally influential center of art, culture, fashion and finance.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <h4 class="location-tag">Reykjavik</h4>
        <%= image_tag("bluelagoon.jpg", size: '335x344',class: "img-circle") %>
        <p class="text-muted" style="padding-top: 50px">Iceland, a Nordic island nation, is defined by its dramatic volcanic landscape of geysers, hot springs, waterfalls, glaciers and black-sand beaches. The capital, Reykjavik, home to the majority of the population, runs on geothermal power and offers a renowned nightlife scene as well as Viking history museums.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <h4 class="location-tag">Tokyo</h4>
        <%= image_tag("tokyo.jpg", size: '335x344', class: "img-circle") %>
        <p class="text-muted" style="padding-top: 50px">Tokyo, Japanâ€™s bustling capital, mixes the ultramodern and the traditional, from neon-lit skyscrapers and anime shops to cherry trees and temples. The opulent Meiji Shinto Shrine is known for its towering gate and surrounding forests.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<hr>

<!-- Just for the weekend -->
<section id="explore" style="padding-top: 50px; padding-bottom: 100px">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
          <h2 class="section-heading">Just for the weekend </h2>
          <h3 class="section-subheading text-muted" style="padding-bottom: 30px">Discover new, inspiring places close to home</h3>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row text-center">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <h4 class="location-tag">Bali</h4>
        <%= image_tag("bali.jpg", size: '335x344',class: "img-circle") %>
        <p class="text-muted" style="padding-top: 50px">The culture of Bali is unique. People say that the Balinese people have reached self-content. This is still reflected in days to day life and can be seen in the numerous ceremonies, Balinese festivals and magnificent temples and palaces. </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <h4 class="location-tag">Koh Phi Phi</h4>
        <%= image_tag("kohphiphi.jpg", size: '335x344', class: "img-circle") %>
        <p class="text-muted" style="padding-top: 50px">One of the most unique and attractive clusters of islands in the world, Koh Phi Phi is an idyllic island retreat that features a number of beaches that feature a variety of accommodation options and many outdoor activities.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <h4 class="location-tag">Ubud</h4>
        <%= image_tag("ubud.jpg", size: '335x344', class: "img-circle") %>
        <p class="text-muted" style="padding-top: 50px">Ubud is Bali's cultural heart. This area is located in the cool mountains, just one hour's drive north of the airport and the resorts of southern Bali, this traditional country town is the home of the Balinese Royal family.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>